    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, powered by the 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. This unit exhibits flawless boost response across the rev range, with the primary and secondary Hitachi turbos engaging with factory precision. The chassis retains its legendary 50/50 weight distribution, complemented by a Torsen limited-slip differential and aluminum double-wishbone suspension for unparalleled kinematic feedback. Every component, from the uncracked dash to the original Montego Blue paint, reflects a vehicle kept in a climate-controlled environment. Mechanically stock and cosmetically peerless, it represents the pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
