      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector's dream, maintained in showroom condition since day one. The exterior features a flawless, deep-gloss finish with absolutely no swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent, with premium leather upholstery that shows zero wear or creasing. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is impeccable; it has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a full paper trail of preventative maintenance. Garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather, the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new example of this model.",
